cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.NI, cs.SE, cs.DL

This paper discusses the analysis of modern blockchains, which involves topics related to computer security (cs.CR), distributed computing (cs.DC), network infrastructure (cs.NI), software engineering (cs.SE), and machine learning (cs.DL) in terms of smart contract design. The paper also presents a crawler for Ethereum, which falls under the category of network infrastructure (cs.NI). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CR, followed by cs.DC, cs.NI, cs.SE, and cs.DL.
